# TIME BEYOND US - Development Status

## Latest Update: v68.0.0 - iOS Capabilities & Admin Panel (2025-12-27)

### SECURITY FIX APPLIED
- Removed exposed Apple app-specific passwords from batch files
- GitGuardian incident resolved
- Passwords must now be set via environment variables or EAS secrets
- **ACTION REQUIRED**: Revoke old app-specific passwords in Apple ID settings

### iOS BUILD STATUS
- Build #5 ERRORED - Same certificate import issue
- Error: "Distribution certificate hasn't been imported successfully"
- The certificate exists but EAS can't import it to the build keychain
- **SOLUTION**: Need to regenerate iOS credentials via `eas credentials`

### COMPLETED FEATURES

#### Master Admin Feature Control Panel (/admin/features)
- Full CRUD for feature flags
- Enable/disable toggles
- Rollout percentage slider (0-100%)
- User segment targeting (all, premium, free, beta_testers, by_country)
- Announcement system on feature enable
- Real-time stats dashboard

#### Auto-Announcement System
- Automatic announcements when features are enabled
- Push notification broadcast
- In-app banner with customizable types (info, success, warning, feature)
- Duration control (1-30 days)
- Announcement preview

#### User Segment Targeting
- Segment-based feature rollout
- Percentage-based gradual rollout
- Geographic targeting support
- Beta tester targeting

#### iOS Capabilities Added (app.json)
- Sign In with Apple
- In-App Purchases (merchant ID configured)
- HealthKit integration
- Siri integration
- NFC Tag Reading
- iCloud sync
- Location services
- Background modes (notifications, fetch, processing)

